viewData.name: Smokey Eyes Eyelashes 41
viewData.short_description: The PhiNesse eyelashes are natural and handmade. Each eyelash is made to look as natural as possible.
viewData.long_description: The PhiNesse eyelashes are natural and handmade. Each eyelash is made to look as natural as possible. The eyelashes are soft, flexible, easy to apply and comfortable to wear. PhiNesse Smokey Eye eyelashes are designed to achieve the particular Smokey moment. These eyelashes are suitable for all types of eyes.
